Post card moments from Egypt’s beach paradise 🏖️ 
📍 Sharm El Sheikh 

Day 1: Checked into White Hills Resort 🌴 spent the day just soaking it all in and exploring the place.
Day 2: Went deep sea diving 🤿 the underwater world out here is serene
Day 3: Chilled at Farsha Café with some epic views, then hit up Dolce Vita and partied all night 💃 

Sharm, you were a vibe. 🌊🌅🎉
